## ğŸ”§ What packages.txt Does:

Streamlit Cloud will install these system packages:
- **freetds-dev** - FreeTDS library for SQL Server
- **freetds-bin** - FreeTDS binaries
- **unixodbc** - ODBC driver manager
- **unixodbc-dev** - ODBC development files

These provide the ODBC drivers needed to connect to Azure SQL!

